d","tid":2085944,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:19:21.000Z","msg":"【「和你做筆友」計劃 小結】<br />\n<br />\n「和你做筆友」計劃現共有78名手足參與，並成功配對了207對筆友，謝謝大家對手足的關心！<br />\n<br />\n「和你做筆友」計劃持續進行中，歡迎各位寫信撐手足！<br />\n<br />\n參與和你做筆友計劃，請把信寄到：<br />\n邵家臻立法會議員辦事處<br />\n香港中區立法會道1號立法會綜合大樓1018室<br />\n(Room 1018, Legislative Council Complex, 1 Legislative Council Road, Central, Hong Kong)<br />\n<br />\n「和你做筆友」計劃 Q&amp;A：<br />\nshorturl.at/hJKM2 <br />\n<br />\n邵家臻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tuFocnL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtuFocnL.jpg&h=cd970518&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20978d650a262c48d1caf3c0ecb8116861c97047","tid":2085944,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:20:09.000Z","msg":"行動之外都要留意還押緊既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推送同路人、被捕人士相關新聞及資訊<br />\n<br />\n【關注組】 @youarenotalonehk<br />\n【直播台】 @youarenotalonehk_live<br />\n【資訊部】 @youarenotalonehk_info<br />\n【搜證部】 @youarenotalonehk_evidence<br />\n【收信部】 @youarenotalonehk_mailbox<br />\n【法庭時間表】<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2psqNvm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2psqNvm&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CCHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=9be29084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2psqNvm</a>"},{"pid":"2fcccac76333ba4b4567f0bd21a97a6f07bd65c5","tid":2085944,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/pig.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/pig.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/pig.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"eeaab2523e5644babb28af79d7a09119c5cbb943","tid":2085944,"uid":70489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:22:04.000Z","msg":"推 聽日維園見"},{"pid":"1c44a3e171843e225d898e2b912a6be08e038fc5","tid":2085944,"uid":151469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446919538c0bd2b4d909815614111fa377efaa87","tid":2085944,"uid":244614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c44a3e171843e225d898e2b912a6be08e038fc5","tid":2085944,"uid":151469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:26:14.000Z","msg":"推 聽日維園見"},{"pid":"d4ced79118e9779ae5a8cd364e4b3133a1218ce8","tid":2085944,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:28:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8d32e71da7fb09cbf78830abe10e54fa515bf4","tid":2085944,"uid":244614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6a18ddc9e62e601c5d1869b1ebc743249e4923c","tid":2085944,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:02:53.000Z","msg":"#手足投稿 #一定要睇<br />\n<br />\n《前線手足留比香港人既口信，71見！》<br />\n<br />\n其實都抗爭左成年啦！我諗大家都會明白&mdash;&mdash;光復香港<br />\n唔係淨係食黃店 repo下文宜<br />\n咁就光復到香港，而係做出黎，我哋已經再冇退路。<br />\n<br />\n我再懇請大家記得&mdash;&mdash;香港人，呢個身份真係有今生無來世。<br />\n未有反送中風波之前，我諗我真係一隻好完整既港豬<br />\n但呢次唔同，一次又一次係眼前既警暴、朋友既失蹤，下意識到好大件事，但我唔覺得自已做錯野！<br />\n捍衛自由，係我哋既目的。<br />\n<br />\n但7 1國安法就正式打到黎，<br />\n乜野分裂國家罪、判國罪，大家都會被例入黑名單；大家要面對既可能一生既。<br />\n監獄生活，什至送中<br />\n白色恐怖，已經最大化<br />\n中共既高壓打手段，加上警察既濫打、濫捕，我哋真係唔反抗咩？<br />\n但我哋都係人都會攰，為捍自由不惜一切！<br />\n<br />\n但我希望7月1見到大家出黎！<br />\n假如7月1再失敗，證明我亦會返回原來既生活，希望7月1見到你哋 ！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n香港人，反抗！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hknimC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FhknimC&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CCHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=7eb4df80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hknimC</a> <br />\n<br />\n仲有條片！大家入去睇下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:29:41.000Z","msg":"lihkg-app://asset/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif"},{"pid":"91aacfe902a879a03bad19d5cd639edeca9eba72","tid":2085944,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:29:43.000Z","msg":"⚠️手足被控管有攻擊性武器<br />\n⚠️請大家幫手spread出去所有平台<br />\n<br />\n編號：#EVI062<br />\n案發日期：2019年11月11日<br />\n案發時間：7:00 - 8:00 AM<br />\n案發地點：#旺角 彌敦道687號<br />\n需要影片：需要任何於上述時間拍攝到的影片 (最好有影片擁有者)<br />\n<br />\n如果你當時在場請聯絡: <br />\nTelegram: @lllxxxxxxxlll / @whydontyoujustkillusall<br />\nEmail: fthepopo.dllm@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YmcFeEx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYmcFeEx.jpg&h=28735428&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01c7805bcf37c851fa5e37c34de580b380ee8dea","tid":2085944,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:30:19.000Z","msg":"你若放棄，誰衛我城<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e19acc9bb7502d8555d13d37af5b6653a4ce2fe8","tid":2085944,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:30:47.000Z","msg":"推到聽日銅鑼灣爆人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5730138da320f94f0830d8e8ef36456deb09842a","tid":2085944,"uid":244614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e19acc9bb7502d8555d13d37af5b6653a4ce2fe8","tid":2085944,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:30:47.000Z","msg":"推到聽日銅鑼灣爆人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\