,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:30:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/pig.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今晚各區都有悼念活動 大家留意"},{"pid":"5849ed291737cbb6912aaa4521eb8cbaccce655e","tid":2085944,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"765bb396797e75b2b412fabb57f388a9e55615c2","tid":2085944,"uid":244614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5849ed291737cbb6912aaa4521eb8cbaccce655e","tid":2085944,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:32:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"210484d19fa3d3cd7ee5cc8e47645c2ec1599814","tid":2085944,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:39:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/pig.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/pig.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/pig.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0ac41ea17fbf614e70111c6c3553c9b095d5f1","tid":2085944,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:45:28.000Z","msg":"【重光之路】<br />\n<br />\n本來，今日嘅難關係2047年末代香港人要獨自面對嘅難題。單憑末代香港人，對中共簡直毫無還擊之力。<br />\n<br />\n平衡時空下，溫水煮蛙，末代香港人以獨力難支，潰不成軍作結。<br />\n<br />\n而家，反而係將末代香港人單獨面對嘅重擔，由幾代香港人共同分擔、面對、攬炒，繼而浴火重生。<br />\n<br />\n喺依一個時空，香港民族經歷整整一年時代革命洗禮，已經將殊死不屈、攬炒中共嘅意志注入靈魂，刻進骨髓。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一年前，送中法壓境；當時不論本土、國際都無意慾以攬炒中共作為反制手段。<br />\n<br />\n一年後，國安法降臨；香港本土攬炒中共嘅意志已經形成，甚至席捲全球；國際社會亦決意制裁中共。<br />\n<br />\n前路彷佛難行，但我地已經為一個香港創造咗一個有機會重光嘅未來。Keep calm and carry on.<br />\n<br />\n願 榮光歸香港<br />\n願 香港民族 亂流下平安<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; 攬炒巴字<br />\n2020年6月30日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n攬炒團隊《重光計劃》<br />\n<br />\n正牌攬炒Channel🔥<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/StirFryChannel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FStirFryChannel&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CCHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=86745224\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/StirFryChannel</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iU44GKN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiU44GKN.jpg&h=f0ba24ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca2b76143fbb544d0bf69a3982265b562b0b20ba","tid":2085944,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:47:20.000Z","msg":"面對著極權的政府，香港人在過去一年經歷了回歸二十二年以來從沒有發生的事。警暴，政治審查，打壓新聞及言論自由等等，香港人已經見慣了。雖然國安法將於明天通過，相信連串打壓審查行動將再次升級。<br />\n<br />\n在一年前，200萬+1 人懷著相同的信念走上街頭爭取民主。一年後，我們雖然面對著極權的打壓，請記得我們都是熱愛這片土地的人，我們都是一起為著相同信念進發的。 <br />\n<br />\n或許明天是一個重要的轉捩點，但不會是我們終結。只要香港人還在，抗爭永遠不會完結，讓真相繼續流傳，讓我們一起創造出一段又一段屬於香港人的歷史吧！ <br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n港島東鷹眼仝人字<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/easternhawkeye\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Feasternhawkeye&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CCHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=d1ac5ec6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/easternhawkeye</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6gfLrb2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6gfLrb2.jpg&h=29d68d9b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2622a1fcaa21fd071498d817fd76bc89057ad24","tid":2085944,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cd3dd0fb4b3a5738e6a5910e327ad3d989f3064","tid":2085944,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:55:55.000Z","msg":"我宣佈：今日，係港獨運動嘅開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2086124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2086124</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7563b14639cec42de25aed38ad8ca09626b847da","tid":2085944,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:59:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d3a5fa01d206e146bff72538dbec90041502e5e","tid":2085944,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b7dde0dce22ef83cdbb64243523411fbe8ec321","tid":2085944,"uid":296410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:13:00.000Z","msg":"好有endgame嘅感覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae2059ae7551738e37ee7f0c91a5999403f185c","tid":2085944,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b7dde0dce22ef83cdbb64243523411fbe8ec321","tid":2085944,"uid":296410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:13:00.000Z","msg":"好有endgame嘅感覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />宜家先係開始"},{"pid":"bc22a5c26a5b6a96bfc2efb554bd689f9ae675ba","tid":2085944,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:24:27.000Z","msg":"係呢個大是大非，香港面臨極權打壓下，我地團隊同大家承諾，我地一定堅持到底，撐到最後一刻。<br />\n<br />\n            我地希望所有香港朋友，無論和理非勇武還是海外手足或身處香港也好，堅守獨立自主的普世價值觀。曾經何時，歐洲強國法國有一半領土也淪陷於德國。但係海外法國人無因此而放棄，反而用各種方式抗爭到底，1945年法國光復了。<br />\n<br />\n            世上沒難事，只要堅持，凡事就有轉機。<br />\n<br />\n     香港人，加油！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />囝搵老豆老母"},{"pid":"701c20d4f5f2ad33bfe60599d0f4e1c084fb7896","tid":2085944,"uid":89923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:25:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}